News.headline: Supporters Coach Travel For FC Halifax Town
News.page_title: Supporters Coach Travel For FC Halifax Town
News.URL_keywords: Supporters Coach Travel For FC Halifax Town
News.short_description: Information regarding the supporters coach that will be travelling to tomorrow's Emirates FA Cup replay against FC Halifax Town.
News.description:
The supporters have a coach for the Emirates FA Cup replay on Tuesday and there is still time to book your place on the coach for the trip. 

The coach will be departing Victoria Road at 12:30pm and prices for the travel are £23.00, so book your place on the coach to support the Daggers now. 

To book your place, or if you have any further questions, please call the Supporters Club travel Hotline on: 07989901686.
